<title>
Clutch Fluid Inspection (M/T Model)
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check clutch system for sign of fluid leakage. Repair leaky point if any.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check reservoir for fluid level. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENBP70A5306006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If fluid is lower than minimum level of reservoir, refill reservoir with specified brake fluid indicated on reservoir cap.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A020004.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "61.033mm" ver = "01" gw = "227" gh = "156"/>
